WEBVTT

00:01:59.281 --> 00:02:02.270
Ulimwengu ungekuwa wa giza
na wa baridi zaidi,

00:02:02.270 --> 00:02:03.650
ukikaribia hali ya kuganda

00:02:03.650 --> 00:02:05.500
unaojulikanana kama Ubaridi Mkubwa,

00:02:05.500 --> 00:02:08.380
au kifo cha joto cha Ulimwengu.

00:02:08.380 --> 00:02:11.340
Lakini inakuwaje kama nguvu muasi
ni kubwa sana

00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:15.080
kufanya kamba ya mpira ipanuke kupita
kipimo chake,

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.870
na iichane kabisa?

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:19.990
Kama kutanuka kwa ulimwengu
kunazidi kuongezeka,

00:02:19.990 --> 00:02:23.760
itaweza kuzidi sio tu 
nguvu ya uvutano --

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:26.480
ikichana galaksi na mifumo ya jua--

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:30.960
lakini pia na nguvu hafifu ya sumaku
umeme,na nguvu za nguvu za nuklia